{
  "name": "RPlog_Cochran_Invaded",
  "title": "The Invasion of Cochran",
  "summary": "Newly appointed Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin, broken-backed and commanding from a medical bed aboard the Star Dreadnought Malevolence, springs a surprise three-pronged Imperial assault, Operation Retribution, on the unsuspecting Griffon home fleet over Cochran. The Griffon defenders scramble: the silver-haired Captain of the Mako cruiser Gabriel, the Black Eagle's mustachioed captain, and Captain Sesbtain Williams of the Admiral Rishar maneuver to shield the planet and the fleeing civilians. Imperial commanders Felipe del Montefort of the Malignant and the Warlord Vassily Korolov pour concussion-missile fire into the Gabriel, while bomber pilots Seifer Wolf, Tellain, Antilles, and Vorenus dogfight Griffon pilots like Theta One and Dak Storkrom. As Kreldin closes his vise and the Gabriel's shields fail, the doomed flagship's captain orders a ramming run into the Imperial armada; with the New Republic fleet arriving, the surviving Griffon ships fall back to regroup with their allies.",
